Synapse studio:

1️⃣ Azure Synapse — simplest way
Goal

Run SQL query directly on CSV stored in Blob Storage.

Steps (very short)
Go to Azure Portal
Search Azure Synapse Analytics
Click Create
Fill:
Workspace name → synapse1
Region → same as storage
Storage account → select your blob storage
Click Create

Wait 2–3 min ⏳

Run query
Click Open Synapse Studio
Click Develop
Click + → SQL script
Paste:
SELECT TOP 5 *
FROM OPENROWSET(
    BULK 'https://<storage-name>.blob.core.windows.net/data/house_price_dataset.csv',
    FORMAT='CSV',
    PARSER_VERSION='2.0',
    FIRSTROW=2
) AS data;
Click Run

Done ✅

No table creation needed.
